@{u}BRICKS@{uu}

  There are 12 different types of bricks. Have a look at the in-game doc.

@{b}«Normal» bricks:@{ub} they are destroyed after the first hit. 14
different colors are available: blue, light blue, blue-green, cyan,
green, yellow, orange, red, purple, violet, grey, white, pink and skin.

@{b}Two shot bricks:@{ub} similar to the normal ones, these bricks have a
rectangle drawn on it. They become "normal" at the first contact with a
ball. There're 14 different colors.

@{b}Three shot bricks;@{ub}

@{b}Unbreakable bricks:@{ub} grey, in the form of a truncated pyramid.
Can't be broken, except by taking the right bonus (thunder) or by using
the superlaser. They can also be destroyed thanks to explosive bricks.
Finally, thanks to others bonus we can transform them into normal or two
shot bricks.

@{b}Explosive bricks:@{ub} yellow, flashing, they explode when they collide
with a ball. They destroy all the bricks in contact with them in one single
shot - including unbreakable and other explosive bricks.

@{b}Invisible bricks:@{ub} they appear at the first contact with a ball.

@{b}Invulnérable bricks:@{ub} gray, can NEVER be destroyed...

@{b}Explosive bricks downward:@{ub} similar to the explosive ones, but only
destroy the bricks located in the same column. The explosion is stopped
by invulnerable bricks and by the edges.


@{b}Explosive bricks upward;@{ub}

@{b}Explosive bricks towards left:@{ub} similar to the explosuve ones, but
only destroy the bricks located in the same row and at the left. The
explosion is stopped by invulnerable bricks and by the edges.

@{b}Explosive bricks towards right;@{ub}

@{b}One Side bricks:@{ub} destroyed in a single shot when they are hit in
the direction of the arrow. Otherwise, they are unbreakable. They can be
destroyed using laser in any direction.

@{b}«Bumper» bricks:@{ub} red, flashing and invulnerable, they increase
the speed of the ball which touch them.

But also:

@{b}Bicolor bricks@{ub} (just for fun) which are similar to the normal
ones...

@{b}'LEGO' ® like bricks@{ub} (ditto)

@{u}** NOTE:@{uu} when all the bricks at the center of the screen are
destroyed, the lamps DANGER are switched on. At any moment, a (small) bat
can go out by the top or the bottom of the screen and cross the game area.
