@{u}PAUSE AND OPTIONS@{uu}
  During the game, you can make a PAUSE by pressing the HELP key.
Then, there're three options available:

 - F1 or FIRE: continue game.

 - F3: give up the game and go back to menu.

 - F5: give up the game and go back to Workbench (don't save options).

@endnode

