@{u}BEGIN A GAME@{uu}

  When you have selected START, a player(s) selection window appear on
the Workbench Screen (only 4 colours are needed).

  You @{b}MUST@{ub} enter a name before playing. You can:

 - create a new player by clicking on "CREATE NEW" (or pressing C); then,
   enter the name (8 letters at most) and click on "OK" to confirm (or
   press O). A new file is ceated in the ABD:players directory with the
   .abdp extention.

 - load a saved player by clicking on "LOAD" or by pressing the L key.
   Select the player thanks to the file requester and click on OK to
   confirm.

  When a player have been selected, his stats are displayed in the window.
Click on "OK" to play.
@endnode

