@{u}BEGIN OF A ROUND@{uu}

  Before each round, ABD choose a level between the available ones. This
one is displayed, and its features are shown at the top of the screen
before you push FIRE:

  - number of the round

  - number of the level

  If you want to go back to the menu, press ESC. Press FIRE if you want
to start the game. Pressing DEL allows you to select another level.A
window appear on the WB screen. You can:

  - click on "CANCEL" (or press C) to cancel the operation;

  - click on "RANDOM" (or prees R) to choose another level at random;

  - enter a number in the text window; then, click on "OKAY" (or press O)
    to continue. Of course, the number MUST be smaller than the number
    of available levels which is displayed at the bottom of the window.

@endnode

