@{u}END OF MATCH@{uu}

  When one of the players win the game, the stats are displayed. Stats
are quite complete:

 - match result (number of wins by players);
 - number of tied rounds;
 - number of goals scored;
 - number of goals by round;
 - number of own goals;
 - own goals %;
 - points;
 - points by round;
 - number of broken bricks;
 - number of taken bonus;
 - number of superbonus;
 - money left.

  The following data are saved for each player:

 - number of games won;
 - number of games lost;
 - best result;
 - best score;
 - number of rounds played;
 - goals per round.

@endnode

